description: If you see Zameen zoomin’ through Santa Cruz, it feasibly means that you’re in for a feast of amazing Mediterranean cuisine. This gilded truck is serving up ancient Eastern Mediterranean food with a delicious modern twist. You can taste the tradition when you take a bite of any of their delightful dishes, including their fluffy Falafels, savory Salads, juicy Gyro Wraps, and everything in between.
name: Zameen Cuisine
